title: "Atlas Database"
date: 2020-05-28
---

The first step is to set up the Atlas database - this is the foundation data layer that serve data to the mobile apps, charts, and web apps.

[ ] Login to <A HREF="https://cloud.mongodb.com">cloud.mongodb.com</A> - create a free login if needed.
[] Create a project (example: Code For Good). 
[x] Go to Access Manager, and give yourself all permissions, not just Owner.
[ ] Create a 4.4 Cluster
[ ] Add database access (example: admin)
[ ] Whitelist your IP



